           SHORT="Ambisonic encoding / decoding and binauralization library in C++"

cat << EOF
Ambisonic encoding / decoding and binauralization library in C++ library for Ambisonic
encoding and decoding, filtering and binaural rendering. It is targetted to render
High-Order Ambisonic (HOA) and VR/3D audio samples in multiple environments, from
headphones to classic loudspeakers. Its binaural rendering can be used for classical
5.1/7.1 spatial channels as well as Ambisonics inputs.
EOF
